    "audio": "http://www.ya-mahdi.net/apps_audio/28th.mp3", 
    "transliteration": "ALLAAHUMMA WAFFIR HAZZEE FEEHE MENAN NAWAAFELE WA AKRIMNEE FEEHE BE-EHZAARIL MASAA-ELE WA QARRIB FEEHE WASEELATEE ELAYKA MIM BAYNIL WASAA-ELE YAA MAN LAA YASHGHALOHU IL-HAA-HUL MOLEHHEENA.", 
    "english": "O Allah, on this day, decide for me a share of the supererogatory acts, honor me by making me care for the matters, and make near my means to You from among the other means. O He Whom is not preoccupied by the earnest entreaty of the insisters!"
